  "title": "Storm-Inspired Inventor",
  "secondName": "Storm-Inspired Inventor",
  "description": "Greta is going to change the world someday. Everyone in her village told her so when she was a child, so it must be true. She has everything a visionary needs: a whip-smart mind, a tireless work ethic, and perhaps most importantly, a total lack of common sense. She dreams of one day capturing lightning in a bottle, so that the people of Erden can have as much light as they want, whenever they want.\n\nA traveling Winvy merchant -- who has gone by many names, but who she knows as Mr. Beauregard Chancy -- saw the potential of her idea when she chased him down at the market fair one day. He agreed to put her through sorcery school in exchange for the exclusive right to sell her invention once she has a working model.\n\nIt's been three years. It must be coming any day now.",
